result.longName: Shandong Bohui Paper Industry Co., Ltd.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Shandong Bohui Paper Industry Co., Ltd. researches, develops, produces, sells, imports, and exports paper products in China. The company offers food card series, such as double-sided coated food cards, paper cups, coated paper cups; tobacco card series, which includes high-grade coated cigarette cards and king color fiber anti-counterfeiting cigarette pack; white card series red-crowned crane, including red crowned crane double-sided coated white cards and double-sided coated white cards; and copper card series, such as double-sided copper cards, copper cards, business card, and poker special papers used for clothing tags, desk calendars, high-end brochures, book covers, business cards, playing cards, etc. It also provides whiteboard series; offset printing papers, coated papers, book papers, electrostatic copy papers used in teaching materials, books, student books, and other purposes.; printing papers; and bull card series, such as kraft cardboards, environmental protection kraft cardboards, and white-faced cattle cards for use in daily necessities, hardware and electrical appliances, and other packaging box surface paper purposes; and gypsum facial papers. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Zibo, China.
